<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1373,1974]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,585,1805,1830]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">Composition and distribution.</emphasis>
Seven species from central parts of Southern South America; 
<taxonomicName authority="Grismado &amp; Carrión, 2017" authorityName="Grismado &amp; Carrión" authorityYear="2017" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Almafuerte" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="peripampasica" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">A. peripampasica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[328,393,1843,1866]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
from Argentina and Uruguay, 
<taxonomicName authority="Grismado &amp; Carrión, 2017" authorityName="Grismado &amp; Carrión" authorityYear="2017" box="[758,855,1842,1866]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Almafuerte" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="facon" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[758,855,1842,1866]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">A. facon</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[873,938,1843,1866]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
from Cochabamba, Bolivia, and five only known from Argentina: 
<taxonomicName authority="(Gerschman &amp; Schiapelli)" authorityName="Gerschman &amp; Schiapelli" box="[431,827,1877,1902]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Echemus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="giaii">
<emphasis box="[431,516,1878,1902]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">A. giaii</emphasis>
(Gerschman &amp; Schiapelli)
</taxonomicName>
from Santa Fe, 
<taxonomicName authority="Grismado &amp; Carrión, 2017" authorityName="Grismado &amp; Carrión" authorityYear="2017" box="[1019,1131,1878,1902]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Almafuerte" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="remota" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[1019,1131,1878,1902]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">A. remota</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1149,1214,1879,1902]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, from Santiago del Estero and Mendoza, 
<emphasis box="[402,494,1914,1939]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">
<taxonomicName authority="Grismado &amp; Carrión, 2017" authorityName="Grismado &amp; Carrión" authorityYear="2017" box="[402,490,1914,1939]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Almafuerte" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kuru" status="n. sp.">A. kuru</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[503,568,1915,1938]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, from Santiago del Estero, 
<taxonomicName authority="Grismado &amp; Carrión, 2017" authorityName="Grismado &amp; Carrión" authorityYear="2017" box="[885,1019,1914,1939]" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Almafuerte" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="goloboffi" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis box="[885,1019,1914,1939]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">A. goloboffi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1036,1098,1915,1938]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
from Salta and Jujuy, and 
<taxonomicName authority="Grismado &amp; Carrión, 2017" authorityName="Grismado &amp; Carrión" authorityYear="2017" class="Arachnida" family="Gnaphosidae" genus="Almafuerte" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="vigorosa" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="267">A. vigorosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[262,323,1951,1974]" pageId="4" pageNumber="267" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, from Corrientes.
</paragraph>
